inary Run\n2 data there are hints of the decays $H \\rightarrow ZZ$ in the golden channel.\nWe also critically discuss plausible reasons for the discrepancies between the\ntwo LHC experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Oct 2022 17:32:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Oct 2022 06:51:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 2 Nov 2022 07:08:37 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 17 Dec 2022 10:58:35 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Fri, 20 Jan 2023 07:32:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-23"}
